 S. 9th Streets).Decorating stations will be set up in the SJWC Landmark Ballroom. If you''d like, participate in our Gingerbread House Decorating Contest at 4:00 p.m. Prizes for the best house in several age categories and a ribbon for all participants.It''s our thirteenth year at the SJWC. Proceeds from the Gingerbread House Decorating Party benefit local charities such as Child Advocates of Silicon Valley, Family Supportive Housing, Inc, The Grateful Garment Project and Silicon Valley Pet Project.Special thanks to our sponsors, Phil Ma Realtor, Naglee Park Campus Community Association. Sponsorship opportunities available. For more information, call 408-294-6919 or email gingerbread@sjwomansclub.org.Read moreCategory: Holiday, Christmas','https://www.eventbrite.com/e/13th-annual-gingerbread-house-decorating-party-tickets-1839264643059?aff=ebdssbdestsearch',NULL,'eventbrite','festival',0,'2025-11-19T23:28:13.992Z','2025-11-24_to_2025-11-30',0,'ç¬¬åä¸‰å±Šå§œé¥¼å±‹è£…é¥°æ´¾å¯¹');
