INSERT INTO events VALUES(314,'Mochi Factory Tour, Sun. Dec. 7th','mochi factory tour sun dec 7th','2025-12-07T17:00:00.000Z',NULL,'1621 Fifth St, 1621 Fifth Street, Berkeley, CA 94710','$11.44','JOIN US FOR A BEHIND THE SCENES SENSORY EXPERIENCE & GET TO KNOW THE MOCHI MUFFIN STORY UP CLOSE AND PERSONAL WITH THE FOUNDERS!JOIN US FOR A BEHIND THE SCENES SENSORY EXPERIENCE & GET TO KNOW THE MOCHI MUFFIN ORIGIN STORY UP CLOSE AND PERSONAL WITH THE FOUNDERS!A personal walkthrough of the creation of the Original Mochi Muffin and listen to stories from the founders themselves.Guests will tour the baking facility and see where and how all the thousands of famous Mochi Muffins are produced','JOIN US FOR A BEHIND THE SCENES SENSORY EXPERIENCE & GET TO KNOW THE MOCHI MUFFIN STORY UP CLOSE AND PERSONAL WITH THE FOUNDERS!JOIN US FOR A BEHIND THE SCENES SENSORY EXPERIENCE & GET TO KNOW THE MOCHI MUFFIN ORIGIN STORY UP CLOSE AND PERSONAL WITH THE FOUNDERS!A personal walkthrough of the creation of the Original Mochi Muffin and listen to stories from the founders themselves.Guests will tour the baking facility and see where and how all the thousands of famous Mochi Muffins are produced each day. Guests will have the opportunity to learn about the specialty ingredients that goes into each pastry and learn the rich history behind these ingredients as well. And most importantly, get to taste the one and only Original Mochi Muffin that kicked off the mochi muffin craze.2 tour available: 9am to 9:45am, 10am to 10:45am.Each tour is limited to groups of 15 so reserve early.Location is our HQ at1621 5th Street BerkeleySome things to keep in mind before you purchase-Young children under the age of 12 may not be suitable for this tour as it will be conducted in an active food manufacturing facility with heavy machinery.Tickets are not refundable.All items are gluten free but we are not a certified gluten free facility so those with severe gluten allergies are advised to join at their own di