INSERT INTO events VALUES(320,'Victorian Home Holiday Tours - December 7','victorian home holiday tours december 7','2025-12-07T21:00:00.000Z',NULL,'1000 Fulton St, 1000 Fulton Street, San Francisco, CA 94117','$55.20','THE VICTORIAN ALLIANCE HOLIDAY HOME TOURS ARE DECEMBER 7th TICKETS ARE ON SALE NOW. FOR MORE INFORMATION: https://victorianalliance.org/The Victorian Alliance of San Francisco is once again inviting the public to tour five fantastic Alamo Square homes, full of Victorian splendor and decorated for the holidays.Attendees will have the opportunity on the tour to see the principal rooms of each home, decorated in high-Victorian style, and will learn about the history of the Alamo Square area and','THE VICTORIAN ALLIANCE HOLIDAY HOME TOURS ARE DECEMBER 7th TICKETS ARE ON SALE NOW. FOR MORE INFORMATION: https://victorianalliance.org/The Victorian Alliance of San Francisco is once again inviting the public to tour five fantastic Alamo Square homes, full of Victorian splendor and decorated for the holidays.Attendees will have the opportunity on the tour to see the principal rooms of each home, decorated in high-Victorian style, and will learn about the history of the Alamo Square area and each home (complete with recommended walking paths). Docents in each home and tour leaders will provide stories about the homes, their histories, decorations, and why the homes are decorated in certain ways.The Victorian Alliance of San Francisco Victorian Home Holiday Tours will be held on Sunday, December 7th from 1-5 PM. The locations of the specific homes will be revealed closer to the tour date.The public is invited to view the homes and their holiday decorations for the price of a ticket; proceeds from the ticket sales will help the VASF continue its mission to promote the preservation and restoration of historic architecture in the City.$50 for adults$40 for Members (join at victorianalliance.org)$40 per person for Groups of 10 or more$10 per child ages 11-17, accompanied by a parent or guardianThe Victorian House Tour is an important event for the VASF as it raises funds to support our operations and principally our Grants Committee. The Committee offers grants to repair and restore publicly-accessible elements of San Franciscoâ€™s heritage.Over the last 50 years, the Alliance has donated nearly $500,000 to various preservation projects across San Francisco. Past grants have included funding to repair and restore the Palace of Fine Arts, numerous projects within city parks, and in historic buildings such as gold leafing for the SF downtown Mechanics Library signage, leaded-glass restoration at the Castro Theater, and furniture reupholstery at the Haas-Lilienthal House in collaboration with SF Heritage. Proceeds from the Allianceâ€™s 2018 Lower Haight/Hayes Valley tour were dedicated to helping fund the restoration of WPA-era artist Reuben Kadishâ€™s Dissertation on Alchemy, a fresco on display at the Haight Street Art Center.Read moreCategory: Holiday, Christmas','https://www.eventbrite.com/e/victorian-home-holiday-tours-december-7-tickets-1750861657349?aff=ebdssbdestsearch',NULL,'eventbrite','art',0,'2025-11-25T20:05:56.738Z','2025-12-01_to_2025-12-07',0,'ç»´å¤šåˆ©äºšæ•…å±…å‡æ—¥ä¹‹æ—… - 12æœˆ7æ—¥');
