INSERT INTO events VALUES(328,'Ugly Sweater Pub Crawl San Francisco - SweaterCon','ugly sweater pub crawl san francisco sweatercon','2025-12-07T00:00:00.000Z',NULL,'Mayes Oyster House, 1233 Polk Street, San Francisco, CA 94109','From $6.98','Celebrate the Holidays at SweaterCon, San Francisco''s Ugly Sweater Pub CrawlOn Saturday, December 6, we will be taking over some of the best bars in the city for a jolly ''ol Holiday Pub Crawl complete with cheap drinks, sketchy holiday decorations and even a few gifts for some lucky crawlers. No matter how you celebrate the holidays, throwing back beers, holiday drinks and cruising from bar to bar is something that can be enjoyed by all.','Celebrate the Holidays at SweaterCon, San Francisco''s Ugly Sweater Pub CrawlOn Saturday, December 6, we will be taking over some of the best bars in the city for a jolly ''ol Holiday Pub Crawl complete with cheap drinks, sketchy holiday decorations and even a few gifts for some lucky crawlers. No matter how you celebrate the holidays, throwing back beers, holiday drinks and cruising from bar to bar is something that can be enjoyed by all. Feel free to throw on your best ugly Christmas Sweater, Hanukah-inspired gear or whatever tickles your fancy. Santa Costumes, Naughty Elves and other creative get ups are also welcome. Enjoy awesome drink specials at your favorite Polk Street Bars.SweaterCon San FranciscoThe holidays in San Francisco are a time for lights, laughter, and a little bit of mischief. For those who want to embrace the season with a drink in hand, the Ugly Sweater Pub Crawl on Saturday, December 6 offers the perfect opportunity to wear your most ridiculous holiday attire and toast to the spirit of the season.From 4PM to 10PM, take to the streets of San Francisco, hopping between bars decked out in holiday cheer. Whether your sweater features reindeer, Santaâ€™s sleigh, or blinking lights, itâ€™s a chance to celebrate the season in styleâ€”or at least in questionable taste.The evening starts at Mayes Oyster House (1233 Polk Street), the official check-in hub for the event. Here, participants will receive their event wristbands, maps, and festive party favors before setting off to explore more than 10 of the cityâ€™s best bars. From cozy dives to lively lounges, each stop promises its own brand of holiday magic.Drink Specials & Holiday CheerEvery participating bar at Sweatercon offers exclusive drink specials, so whether youâ€™re sipping spiked eggnog, a craft beer, or a seasonal cocktail, your cup will overflow with good cheer. Add in holiday decorations that transform each venue into a winter wonderland, and youâ€™ve got the perfect festive setting for a toast.Find the Gnome ContestFind the hidden gnomes in participating bars to win some sweet prizes (early Christmas presents...Yay!)Party FavorsFrom jingle bell necklaces to Santa hats, participants will be outfitted with festive accessories to enhance their holiday spiritâ€”and their Instagram photos.Your Holiday Bar Crawl ItineraryWith stops like McTeagueâ€™s, R Bar, and Amsterdam Cafe, the crawl features a mix of classic San Francisco bars and hidden gems. Each venue offers its own unique vibe, from the intimate charm of El Lopo to the retro-inspired energy of Decodance.Some highlights include:Wreck Room: Perfect for games, laughs, and festive cocktails.Lush Lounge: A cozy escape with an unbeatable holiday vibe.Uni Pizza: Because nothing pairs with a cocktail like a slice of pizza.A Festive Prelude to SantaconThe Ugly Sweater Pub Crawl comes just a week before the cityâ€™s famed Santacon, giving holiday lovers a chance to pre-game (or warm up their wardrobes) before the annual sea of Santas takes over San Francisco. While Santacon may focus on red suits and beards, the Ugly Sweater Pub Crawl is all about letting your kitschiest knitwear shine.Event Details: When: Saturday, December 6, 4PM to 10PMWhere to Start: Mayes Oyster House, 1233 Polk Street, San FranciscoTickets Include:Drink specials at all participating barsEntry to all venuesHoliday-themed party favorsAccess to the Find the Gnome ContestDJsand more!Participating Bars: Uni Pizza, Route 101, Wreck Room, Lush Lounge, Zhuzh, Hanaro, Mcteagues, El Lopo, Decodance, R Bar, Mayes, 1217 Sutter, Amsterdam Cafe and more!Read moreCategory: Holiday, Christmas','https://www.eventbrite.com/e/ugly-sweater-pub-crawl-san-francisco-sweatercon-tickets-1113658214699?aff=ebdssbdestsearch',NULL,'eventbrite','market',0,'2025-11-25T20:05:56.755Z','2025-12-01_to_2025-12-07',0,'æ—§é‡‘å±±ä¸‘æ¯›è¡£é…’å§ä¸²æ¸¸ - æ¯›è¡£èŠ‚');
