INSERT INTO events VALUES(414,'Bair Island Volunteer Workday','bair island volunteer workday','2025-12-13T17:00:00.000Z',NULL,'Bair Island Public Parking, 654 Sea Anchor Drive, Redwood City, CA 94063','Free','Join Peninsula Open Space Trust and San Francisco Bay Bird Observatory for this fun and unique opportunity to volunteer at Bair Island.Join Peninsula Open Space Trust and San Francisco Bay Bird Observatory for this fun and unique opportunity to volunteer at the Bair Island Unit of the Don Edwards San Francisco Bay National Wildlife Refuge.Volunteers will be guided by SFBBOâ€™s staff and POST Volunteers, and you will spend the morning weeding invasive plants, or planting native species that will','Join Peninsula Open Space Trust and San Francisco Bay Bird Observatory for this fun and unique opportunity to volunteer at Bair Island.Join Peninsula Open Space Trust and San Francisco Bay Bird Observatory for this fun and unique opportunity to volunteer at the Bair Island Unit of the Don Edwards San Francisco Bay National Wildlife Refuge.Volunteers will be guided by SFBBOâ€™s staff and POST Volunteers, and you will spend the morning weeding invasive plants, or planting native species that will support Bair Islandâ€™s ecosystem.Tools will be provided, and no prior experience or knowledge is necessary. Volunteering at Bair Island helps maintain and increase the biodiversity in Redwood City. Expect to learn a brief history of Bair Island along with some information about tidal wetlands and native/invasive plants.This event will involve lifting, digging, carrying, bending, kneeling, and walking on uneven terrain. Keep an eye out for an email containing information about what to bring, wear, etc!Please also note that this activity is best for children ages 14+. All minors must be accompanied by adults for the entirety of the event. As Bair Island is a preserve, there are no dogs allowed. Thank you!Read moreCategory: Travel & Outdoor, Hiking','https://www.eventbrite.com/e/bair-island-volunteer-workday-tickets-1963531601878?aff=ebdssbcitybrowse',NULL,'eventbrite','other',0,'2025-12-01T23:20:52.382Z','2025-12-08_to_2025-12-14',0,NULL);
